{"abstract": "Mr. Platt previously worked for EMI, whose record labels and publishing arm were involved in huge acquisitions in November. Universal\u2019s deal for the record labels remains under review by European regulators.", "web_url": "https://mediadecoder.blogs.nytimes.com/2012/09/10/jon-platt-powerful-talent-scout-in-urban-music-to-join-warnerchappell/", "snippet": "Mr. Platt previously worked for EMI, whose record labels and publishing arm were involved in huge acquisitions in November. Universal\u2019s deal for the record labels remains under review by European regulators.", "lead_paragraph": "As the dust settles on the $2.2 billion sale of EMI Music Publishing to an investor group led by Sony, Jon Platt, a former EMI executive who is one of the most successful and powerful figures in urban music, is joining Warner/Chappell, the publishing arm of the Warner Music Group.", "source": "The New York Times", "multimedia": [], "headline": {"main": "Jon Platt, Powerful Talent Scout in Urban Music, to Join Warner/Chappell", "kicker": "Media Decoder", "content_kicker": null, "print_headline": "", "name": null, "seo": null, "sub": null}, "keywords": [{"name": "subject", "value": "Mergers, Acquisitions and Divestitures", "rank": 1, "major": "N"}, {"name": "subject", "value": "Music", "rank": 2, "major": "N"}, {"name": "subject", "value": "Rap and Hip-Hop", "rank": 3, "major": "N"}, {"name": "persons", "value": "Jay-Z", "rank": 4, "major": "N"}, {"name": "persons", "value": "Ludacris", "rank": 5, "major": "N"}, {"name": "organizations", "value": "Citigroup Inc", "rank": 6, "major": "N"}, {"name": "organizations", "value": "EMI Group PLC", "rank": 7, "major": "N"}, {"name": "organizations", "value": "European Commission", "rank": 8, "major": "N"}, {"name": "organizations", "value": "Sony Corporation", "rank": 9, "major": "N"}, {"name": "organizations", "value": "SONY/ATV Music Publishing", "rank": 10, "major": "N"}, {"name": "organizations", "value": "Terra Firma Capita